com.qualcomm.robotcore.eventloop.opmode

Class OpModeManagerImpl.DefaultOpMode

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.qualcomm.robotcore.eventloop.opmode.OpMode
      • com.qualcomm.robotcore.eventloop.opmode.OpModeManagerImpl.DefaultOpMode
  • Enclosing class:
    OpModeManagerImpl

    public static class OpModeManagerImpl.DefaultOpMode
extends OpMode
    OpModeManagerImpl.DefaultOpMode is the opmode that the system runs when no user opmode is active. Note that it's not necessarily the case that this opmode runs when a user opmode stops: there are situations in which we can transition directly for one user opmode to another.
